author: xxlemonxcurryxx
title: Okay Set But Not Much To It
review:
Good set overall and not bad for the price but there's not much to the building of it and not much you can really do with it once built but display it.
It also comes apart quite easily due to it essentially just being a stack of 1 by something bricks.
Still worth the buy if you like to have seasonal sets around though, especially given the limited number of halloween themed sets.
